narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: English 114 05 is a great class to build fundamental writing skills that are useful in other courses. Yes, I would recommend this class to anyone who wants to become a better writer.
There are better ways to get a writing credit than ENGL 114.
I would recommend it if you want to improve your writing, but maybe another section with a different topic.
take it, not too hard and you learn a lot
I would definitely recommend Lucian's class if he teaches it again. I've heard in general though, ENGL 115 sections can be hit or miss.
